sg.edu.nus.iss.vmcs.store

Class DrinksStoreItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • sg.edu.nus.iss.vmcs.store.StoreItem
      • sg.edu.nus.iss.vmcs.store.DrinksStoreItem

  • public class DrinksStoreItem
extends StoreItem
    This represent a column of drinks in the vending machine. It can store a drink of any particular brand type. There can be as many DrinksStoreItem as desire in the vending machine. This number will be a configurable item for the vending machine. This will be implemented as an instance of StoreItem.
    Version:
    3.0 5/07/2003
    Author:
    Olivo Miotto, Pang Ping Li
